item.title: Probably Chests Mod
item.description: This mod adds pots and chests that spawn all over the world, but beware as some chests are more than meets the eye. 480,000 + Downloads About The Mod The mod adds many different biome specific pots and chests that spawn all over the world which can contain amazing loot. You can smash the pots to get simple items you need for caving while the rare chests can contain a huge range of items.
